<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='299928' id='t-299928'>And his equipment as well.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='301277' id='t-301277'>Yves, welcome. It is quite amazing.</span>
