<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='319377' id='t-319377'>I don't have feathers.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='321744' id='t-321744'>But I feel like a bird sometimes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='325067' id='t-325067'>It's really an unreal feeling,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='328410' id='t-328410'>because normally you have a big thing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='331109' id='t-331109'>a plane, around you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='333000' id='t-333000'>And when I strap just this little harness,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='338550' id='t-338550'>this little wing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='340130' id='t-340130'>I really have the feeling of being a bird.</span>
</span>
</p>
