<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='345162' id='t-345162'>YR: It was about 20 years ago,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='347305' id='t-347305'>when I discovered free falling.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='349622' id='t-349622'>When you go out of an airplane,
you are almost naked.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='354039' id='t-354039'>You take a position like that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='356126' id='t-356126'>And especially when you take
