<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='359960' id='t-359960'>you have the feeling that you are flying.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='363509' id='t-363509'>And that's the nearest thing to the dream.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='367694' id='t-367694'>You have no machine around you.</span>
