<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376083' id='t-376083'>So the idea was, okay,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='379029' id='t-379029'>keep that feeling of freedom,</span>
